<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧١٨٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5889">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ كَثِيرٍ، </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ هِنْدَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٧٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَتْ لِلنَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> إِنَّ أَبَا سُفْيَانَ رَجُلٌ شَحِيحٌ، فَأَحْتَاجُ أَنْ آخُذَ مِنْ مَالِهِ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> خُذِي مَا يَكْفِيكِ وَوَلَدَكِ بِالْمَعْرُوفِ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>